    {\displaystyle \vartheta _{00}(x)=1+2\sum _{n=1}^{\infty }x^{n^{2}}}
  

  
    
      
        
          ϑ
          
            01
          
        
        (
        x
        )
        =
        1
        +
        2
        
          ∑
          
