    {\displaystyle \vartheta _{01}(x)=1+2\sum _{n=1}^{\infty }(-1)^{n}x^{n^{2}}}
  The regular partition number sequence P(n) has this generating function:

  
    
      
        
          ϑ
          
            00
          
        
        (
